**“great lockdown” in 2021**  
@whiteyedcat

“Sometimes we just gotta light up a cigarette and think about how messed up the situation is at the moment in the tub. I’ve been trying to convince myself that it’s alright, that this is gonna end. Even tho sometimes it feels like this confinement has been immortalized in this hell of a country. Wouldn’t it be good to be able to sleep till we’re out of this mess together”

NOT FOR SALE

parcel.description:
# Welcome to Gutter Studio
## A multi-dimensional art and event space. 

Featuring three unique galleries, a multi-level gathering and event space, plus hidden surprises & experiences.

- **Gutter Sam's Studio** - art from [Gutter Sam](https://twitter.com/lifeinthegutter) & the Gutter Studio collection.
- **NXOEED** - art from visual artist and illustrator, [NXOEED](https://nxoeed.carrd.co/)
- **Art Path Gallery** - a curated collection of NFT artists that rotates throughout the year.
